      "title": "メトホルミン、本当に第一選択でいいの？",
      "style": "accent",
      "content": "日本人の糖尿病と欧米ガイドラインのギャップを考える",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-accent{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d4a4a,#14b8a6);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.main{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;height:540px;padding:0 60px;gap:60px}.left-panel{flex:1}.right-panel{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center}h1{font-size:48px;font-weight:900;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:20px}.subtitle{font-size:24px;opacity:0.85;line-height:1.6}.tag{display:inline-block;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:8px 20px;border-radius:20px;font-size:16px;margin-top:16px;margin-right:8px}.avatar-circle{width:200px;height:200px;border-radius:50%;border:4px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1)}.avatar-circle img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}.author-name{font-size:24px;font-weight:700}.author-title{font-size:16px;opacity:0.8;text-align:center;line-height:1.5;margin-top:4px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;opacity:0.6}</style><div class=\"slide slide-accent\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 1 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"left-panel\"><h1>メトホルミン<br>本当に第一選択で<br>いいの？</h1><div class=\"subtitle\">日本人の糖尿病と<br>欧米ガイドラインのギャップを考える</div><div><span class=\"tag\">糖尿病</span><span class=\"tag\">メトホルミン</span><span class=\"tag\">薬物療法</span></div></div><div class=\"right-panel\"><div class=\"avatar-circle\"><img src=\"/dr-iwatatsu.png\" alt=\"Dr.いわたつ\" onerror=\"this.style.display='none'\"></div><div class=\"author-name\">Dr.いわたつ</div><div class=\"author-title\">糖尿病専門医・指導医<br>内分泌専門医 / 医学博士</div></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 2,
      "title": "「まずメトホルミン」で本当にいいですか？",
      "style": "dark",
      "content": "起：BMI 23の非肥満患者にメトホルミンを出していませんか？",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-dark{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#94a3b8}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:30px}.alert-box{border-left:6px solid #14b8a6;background:rgba(20,184,166,0.08);padding:30px 36px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-bottom:24px}.alert-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#e2e8f0}.point-box{border-left:6px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.08);padding:24px 36px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-top:20px}.point-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.7;color:#fca5a5;font-weight:700}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-dark\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 2 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>「まずメトホルミン」で本当にいいですか？</h2><div class=\"alert-box\"><p>2型糖尿病の初期治療に何を選びますか？<br>欧米ガイドラインの答えは「メトホルミン」<br>でも目の前の患者はBMI 23の非肥満<br>インスリン分泌が低下した日本人</p></div><div class=\"point-box\"><p>「ガイドラインでメトホルミン第一選択だから」<br>その思考停止が、最適な治療を遠ざけているかもしれません</p></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 3,
      "title": "UKPDS 34 ── メトホルミン神話の原点",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "承：エビデンスの中身を知っていますか？",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#0a1a1a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:24px}.card{border:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3);border-radius:16px;padding:24px 30px;margin-bottom:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,0.8)}.card-title{font-size:24px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:8px}.card-body{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155}.highlight{color:#14b8a6;font-weight:700}.point-box{border-left:6px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.05);padding:20px 30px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;margin-top:12px}.point-box p{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#dc2626;font-weight:700}.source{font-size:18px;color:#64748b;margin-top:12px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 3 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>UKPDS 34 ── メトホルミン神話の原点</h2><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">対象：過体重の白人 1,704名（1998年）</div><div class=\"card-body\">糖尿病関連エンドポイント <span class=\"highlight\">32%減</span><br>糖尿病関連死亡 <span class=\"highlight\">42%減</span> / 全死亡 <span class=\"highlight\">36%減</span><br>心筋梗塞 <span class=\"highlight\">39%減</span></div></div><div class=\"card\"><div class=\"card-title\">10年追跡（Legacy Effect）</div><div class=\"card-body\">全死亡 <span class=\"highlight\">27%減</span> / 心筋梗塞 <span class=\"highlight\">33%減</span> が持続</div></div><div class=\"point-box\"><p>日本人・アジア人は1人も含まれていない。非肥満患者へのエビデンスの外挿には限界がある</p></div><div class=\"source\">出典：UKPDS Group. Lancet 1998;352:854-865</div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 4,
      "title": "日本人の糖尿病は「別の病態」",
      "style": "dark",
      "content": "転：インスリン分泌障害主体 vs 抵抗性主体",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-dark{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0a1a1a,#132e2e);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#2dd4bf}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#94a3b8}.main{padding:20px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;gap:40px;align-items:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:20px}.col{flex:1}.col-title{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;color:#2dd4bf;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:center;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:2px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.3)}.item{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#e2e8f0;margin-bottom:14px;padding-left:16px;border-left:3px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.4)}.divider{width:2px;background:rgba(20,184,166,0.3);height:80%}.point-box{border-left:6px solid #ef4444;background:rgba(239,68,68,0.08);padding:20px 30px;border-radius:0 16px 16px 0;position:absolute;bottom:80px;left:60px;right:60px}.point-box p{font-size:24px;color:#fca5a5;font-weight:700}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#64748b}</style><div class=\"slide slide-dark\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 4 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><div class=\"col\"><div class=\"col-title\">欧米型</div><div class=\"item\">高度肥満（BMI 30以上）</div><div class=\"item\">インスリン抵抗性が主体</div><div class=\"item\">分泌能は比較的保たれている</div><div class=\"item\">心血管疾患の罹患率が高い</div></div><div class=\"divider\"></div><div class=\"col\"><div class=\"col-title\">日本人型</div><div class=\"item\">軽度肥満〜非肥満（BMI 25未満が約半数）</div><div class=\"item\">インスリン分泌障害が主体</div><div class=\"item\">分泌能が遺伝的に低い</div><div class=\"item\">心血管疾患の罹患率は低い</div></div></div><div class=\"point-box\"><p>メトホルミンは「抵抗性改善薬」。分泌障害主体の日本人には病態の核心を突いていない可能性</p></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 5,
      "title": "病態で選ぶ第一選択薬",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "結：日本糖尿病学会アルゴリズムに基づく個別化",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#0a1a1a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:20px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:24px}.list-item{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:18px}.list-num{font-size:26px;font-weight:900;color:#14b8a6;min-width:50px;margin-right:16px;background:rgba(20,184,166,0.1);width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center}.list-text{font-size:24px;line-height:1.6;color:#334155}.highlight{color:#14b8a6;font-weight:700}.source{font-size:18px;color:#64748b;margin-top:16px}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 5 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>病態で選ぶ第一選択薬</h2><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">1</span><span class=\"list-text\"><span class=\"highlight\">肥満あり</span>（インスリン抵抗性主体）<br>→ メトホルミン / SGLT2阻害薬 / GLP-1 RA</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">2</span><span class=\"list-text\"><span class=\"highlight\">非肥満</span>（インスリン分泌障害主体）<br>→ DPP-4阻害薬 / グリニド薬</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">3</span><span class=\"list-text\"><span class=\"highlight\">ASCVD・心不全・CKD合併</span><br>→ SGLT2阻害薬 / GLP-1 RAを最優先（ADA 2026でも強化）</span></div><div class=\"list-item\"><span class=\"list-num\">4</span><span class=\"list-text\"><span class=\"highlight\">eGFR 30未満</span>の腎機能低下<br>→ メトホルミン禁忌。SGLT2阻害薬やGLP-1 RAを検討</span></div><div class=\"source\">出典：日本糖尿病学会 薬物療法のアルゴリズム第2版 / ADA Standards of Care 2026</div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 6,
      "title": "Take Home Message",
      "style": "accent",
      "content": "3つの持ち帰りポイント",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-accent{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0d4a4a,#14b8a6);color:#fff}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.2);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700}.main{padding:30px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;text-align:center;margin-bottom:40px}.thm-card{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border:2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);border-radius:20px;padding:28px 36px;margin-bottom:24px;display:flex;align-items:center}.thm-num{font-size:36px;font-weight:900;margin-right:24px;min-width:50px;opacity:0.7}.thm-text{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;line-height:1.5}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;opacity:0.6}</style><div class=\"slide slide-accent\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 6 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>Take Home Message</h2><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">01</span><span class=\"thm-text\">UKPDS 34の対象は「過体重の白人」<br>日本人への外挿には限界がある</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">02</span><span class=\"thm-text\">日本人はインスリン分泌障害が主体<br>肥満の有無で病態を評価してから薬剤を選ぶ</span></div><div class=\"thm-card\"><span class=\"thm-num\">03</span><span class=\"thm-text\">心腎リスクにはSGLT2i/GLP-1 RAを優先<br>「全員メトホルミン」は思考停止</span></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
      "num": 7,
      "title": "参考文献",
      "style": "light",
      "content": "論文引用",
      "html": "<style>*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}.slide{width:1280px;height:720px;font-family:'Noto Sans JP',sans-serif;position:relative;overflow:hidden}.slide-light{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f8fffe,#e6f7f5);color:#0a1a1a}.header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:24px 40px}.badge{background:rgba(20,184,166,0.15);padding:6px 18px;border-radius:20px;font-size:15px;color:#0d4a4a}.logo{font-size:15px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.main{padding:20px 60px;height:540px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center}h2{font-size:36px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a;margin-bottom:24px}.ref-item{margin-bottom:14px}.ref-num{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#0d4a4a}.ref-text{font-size:18px;line-height:1.5;color:#334155}.ref-url{font-size:15px;color:#14b8a6;word-break:break-all}.footer{position:absolute;bottom:0;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;padding:16px 40px;font-size:13px;color:#94a3b8}</style><div class=\"slide slide-light\"><div class=\"header\"><span class=\"badge\">Slide 7 / 8</span><span class=\"logo\">Dr.いわたつ</span></div><div class=\"main\"><h2>参考文献</h2><div class=\"ref-item\"><span class=\"ref-num\">1)</span> <span class=\"ref-text\">ADA. Pharmacologic Approaches to Glycemic Treatment: Standards of Care in Diabetes--2026. Diabetes Care 2026;49(Suppl 1):S183-S215</span><br><span class=\"ref-url\">https://doi.org/10.2337/dc26-S009</span></div><div class=\"ref-item\"><span class=\"ref-num\">2)</span> <span class=\"ref-text\">UKPDS Group. Effect of intensive blood-glucose control with metformin on complications in overweight patients with type 2 diabetes (UKPDS 34). Lancet 1998;352:854-865</span><br><span class=\"ref-url\">https://doi.org/10.1016/S0140-6736(98)07037-8</span></div><div class=\"ref-item\"><span class=\"ref-num\">3)</span> <span class=\"ref-text\">Holman RR, et al. 10-year follow-up of intensive glucose control in type 2 diabetes. N Engl J Med 2008;359:1577-1589</span><br><span class=\"ref-url\">https://doi.org/10.1056/NEJMoa0806470</span></div><div class=\"ref-item\"><span class=\"ref-num\">4)</span> <span class=\"ref-text\">日本糖尿病学会. 2型糖尿病の薬物療法のアルゴリズム（第2版）. 糖尿病 2024</span></div><div class=\"ref-item\"><span class=\"ref-num\">5)</span> <span class=\"ref-text\">Chen YC, et al. SGLT2i vs Metformin on CV and Renal Outcomes in Low CV Risk. J Am Heart Assoc 2024;13:e032397</span><br><span class=\"ref-url\">https://doi.org/10.1161/JAHA.123.032397</span></div></div><div class=\"footer\"><span>&copy; Dr.いわたつ</span><span>Dr.いわたつシリーズ</span></div></div>"
    },
    {
